@node Introduction "Autocrop: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   Autocrop is a plugin for the famous Image-Manipulation-Program ArtEffect2+. As
   a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect2+'s menu and waits
   happily for your attention.

   It is able to crop or mask the border of picture, what does come in handy for
   scanned drawings.

   It is also able to crop the picture to the current mask.

@endnode

